snippet.textDisplay: Saw a few episodes of Pimp my Ride back in the day - mostly out of some kind of perverted curiosity of what hellish thing they would create next  - and the one word that I remember them using more than any other was "Monitor". Seems like a few (or many) monitors were their go-to-solution for any problem (or maybe lack of other ideas). The most ridiculous was when they put monitors in the bottom end of the fenders on one of the cars - you had to be lying on the ground to watch...  Great...
